---
title: Cheesy Beef Rissoles & Roasted Veggie Chunks with Smokey Aioli & Garden Salad
description: Rissoles are a crowd-pleasing dinner winner, but when you infuse them with melted Parmesan, they’re even harder to refuse!
This colourful plate also gets a serve of herby roasted veggie chunks and a family-friendly salad for a rainbow of delights.
